#: /tmp/cicero-EpGA/release-9.1.xml:1387(para) 
msgid "This is similar to the existing session-level advisory locks, but the locks are automatically released at transaction end."
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/cicero-EpGA/release-9.1.xml:1394(para) 
msgid "Make <link linkend=\"sql-truncate\"><command>TRUNCATE ... RESTART IDENTITY</command></link> restart sequences transactionally (Steve Singer)"
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/cicero-EpGA/release-9.1.xml:1400(para) 
