#: /tmp/cicero-EpGA/release-9.1.xml:1598(para) 
msgid "Allow binary I/O on type <type>void</type> (Radoslaw Smogura)"
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/cicero-EpGA/release-9.1.xml:1604(para) 
msgid "Improve hypotenuse calculations for geometric operators (Paul Matthews)"
