#: /tmp/cicero-EpGA/release-9.1.xml:1614(para) 
msgid "Support hashing array values (Tom Lane)"
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/cicero-EpGA/release-9.1.xml:1618(para) 
msgid "This provides additional query optimization possibilities."
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/cicero-EpGA/release-9.1.xml:1624(para) 
msgid "Don't treat a composite type as sortable unless all its column types are sortable (Tom Lane)"
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/cicero-EpGA/release-9.1.xml:1629(para) 
msgid "This avoids possible <quote>could not identify a comparison function</quote> failures at runtime, if it is possible to implement the query without sorting. Also, <command>ANALYZE</command> won't try to use inappropriate statistics-gathering methods for columns of such composite types."
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/cicero-EpGA/release-9.1.xml:1645(para) 
msgid "Add support for casting between <type>money</type> and <type>numeric</type> (Andy Balholm)"
