#: /tmp/cicero-EpGA/release-9.1.xml:1652(para) 
msgid "Add support for casting from <type>int4</type> and <type>int8</type> to <type>numeric</type> (Joey Adams)"
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/cicero-EpGA/release-9.1.xml:1659(para) 
